<H2>What's the deal with the PayPal link?</H2>
<P>
Ok, we'd like to keep GuildMagic running. Better still we'd like to keep adding to the system, making it better and better. But hosting the site is very expensive. Until we added the advertising and then paypal donation button we paid for all the hosting out of our own pockets. Even since we added those we've been having to top-up the paypal donations and the advertising revenue with our own cash. So please consider making a voluntary contribution towards our internet connection costs. You can contribute whatever you feel is a fair amount by clicking this PayPal button.
<P>
We've attempted to answer some common questions in the rest of this document.
